<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٦٤٢ -<span class="c5"> نا عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span> أرنا مَعْمَرٌ , عَنْ قَتَادَةَ ,<span class="c5"> فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{يَخِرُّونَ لِلْأَذْقَانِ}</span> <span class="c4">[الإسراء: ١٠٧]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لِلْوُجُوهِ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٦٤٣ -<span class="c5"> قال عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ وَقَالَ مَعْمَرٌ وَقَالَ الْحَسَنُ:</span> <span class="c2">«لِلِّحَى»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>